item.title: Prayer Of Faith
item.dc:creator: naycmedia
item.content:encoded:
Bible Text: Eph 6:18 | Preacher: Kunle Jenmi | Series: Faith and Prayer | Faith is always present Faith is the substance of hope Having a proof of things not seen (Mark 11:24)
What is faith? Faith is the evidence of things not seen. In the place if prayer, faith is activated to believe things asked for even tho after prayer they don't look like they be. ( 2 Cor 4:18) Faith is not of the head but of the heart. When you enter into the place of prayer, when you believe you receive and you'll definitely have it why? Because he calleth those things as tho they were. The challenge is we go into prayer without the word of God and we feel prayer did not work, the reason why prayer will not work is because we have broken the rules.
Everytime you pray, there is an answer on the way already.
The reason why most of us don't pray is because our dream is not bigger than us.

item.title: Change Orchestrated By Balance Character
item.dc:creator: naycmedia
item.content:encoded:
Preacher: Funsho Jenmi | Series: Word Confrence 4.0 | Change orchestrated by balance character After accepting Christ, there is nothing is more important than have the right attitude.
Your attitude can make you happy or miserable for the rest of your life.
Your attitude is key.
1. Your attitude reveal your real self. How important is your attitude? It's more important than your past and more important than your circumstances.
Stress is bound to happen, don't transfer your aggression on someone else.
Your attitude always become your action or reaction.
2. Your attitude determines your relationship and how it is being built. You must have the same attitude that Christ had on earth (Phil 2:5) You attract your kind of person.
Appreciate people's effort
With the right attitude, you can change life

item.title: Forgiveness The Power Of The Gospel 1
item.dc:creator: naycmedia
item.content:encoded:
Bible Text: psalm 130:3-4 | Preacher: Kunle Jenmi | Forgiveness means to pardon that is to say God has pardoned your sins. Every time there's pardon, there's a flow of healing When man fell, man was under the curse of the law and the consequences of the law are death, sicknesses and poverty. In the beginning everything that God created was good, there was no sickness or death everything was perfect. But the sin nature is the reason for sickness.
Forgiveness and paves way for restoration and that restoration brings us back to our original state.
(Rom 1:28) if sin is not convenient, sickness is also not convenient. Originally man is not supposed to sin that's why we feel pain. Every time you give yourself up to carnality the devil strikes and sickness follows. (1 John 3:8) (Numbers 21:6-9) Every time you place your eye on the cross, the devil has no dominion over you.
Your dominion is in the ability to behold.

Purpose is only found in the mind of the creator of a thing, every other person is just guessing. 7. Purpose is the key to fulfilment. Always consult God. Don't put your Bible aside, study it. wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value:
Jremiah 1:5, 1 Timothy 1:9,

 

No human on earth is a mistake. Everyone is created for a reason. 

 

God created no one for entertainment. Go has something in mind for us all. You are not here just for fun. 

 

The only thing that's worse than death is living without purpose. The most important thing for you to find out is "WHY AM I HERE?"

 

There is more to life than just schooling, etc. 

 

WHY makes WHAT important and meaningful. 

 

Purpose is the original intent of the creation of a thing that was in the mind of the creator of that thing.

 

Your purpose is what God had in mind while creating you. 

 

Purpose brings relevance. You cannot fade away when you find and love your purpose. 

 

Potential is different from purpose. Potential is the ability built in a creation to fulfil purpose.

 

7 PRINCIPLES OF PURPOSE.

1. God is a God of purpose. He does all things according to His purpose. 

2. Nothing in life is without a purpose. 

3. Not every purpose is known.

4. When purpose is not known, abuse is inevitable.

5. If you want to know the purpose of a thing, never ask the thing. 

6. Purpose is only found in the mind of the creator of a thing, every other person is just guessing. 

7. Purpose is the key to fulfilment. 

 

Always consult God. Don't put your Bible aside, study it.

 

The wealthiest place on earth is the cemetery because great ideas, goals, vision, insight and creations go inside there unaccomplished. 

 

Will you add to the wealth/ riches in the graveyard or fulfil your purpose on earth?

1 John 5:4, Matthew 14:22-28, Hebrews 1:1-3, Isaiah 43:1-3
Our faith us the victory that overcomes the world. As long as you have faith, you have victory over the world. You are declared an overcomer by the word of God as long as you have faith.
Your faith has won the battle beforehand. Your victory is not directly proportional to the amount of times you prayer but a function/ product of your understanding that you are already an overcomer.
What makes you an overcomer is the fact that you are born of God.
What sustains your faith during the storm is your ability to remember the things that God has done. If you forget the goodness of God, you reduce the capacity of your faith for effectiveness. The foundation of your faith is your ability to praise God in the storm.
The foundation of faith is the Word.

You are a product of your focus i.e what you are looking at. Every distraction is an attraction to something.
Have the God kind of faith. The God kind of faith calls things that are not yet available into existence. Believe in things that are unseen like they are seen. Don't work by sight but by faith. Faith is of the heart.
